pr_title: [GSoC-2021] Experimental VROOM Category functions - vrp_vroom, vrp_vroomJobs, vrp_vroomShipments
pr_body:
Closes #9. This PR adds three new vrpRouting functions: - **vrp_vroom:** Vehicle Routing Problem with VROOM, involving both jobs and shipments. - **vrp_vroomJobs:** Vehicle Routing Problem with VROOM, involving only jobs. - **vrp_vroomShipments:** Vehicle Routing Problem with VROOM, involving only shipments. Additional changes: - Adds style-lint checks to GitHub Actions, and fixes the code checker errors. - Updated NEWS and release_notes for the 3 new vrpRouting VROOM Category functions. This is a final merge PR containing commits from several different PRs combined. The intermediate PRs made on the [GSoC-pgRouting](https://github.com/pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting/) repository are as follows: | Description | Pull Requests | | -----------| --------------------- | |vrp_vroom, vrp_vroomJobs, and vrp_vroomShipments |
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#165
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#167
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#170
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#174

pr_title: [action] adding the actiion update to check updates
pr_body:
Does not necessarily fixes #1892 
Unfortunately if an upgrade file is missing we can not do much about it once its released.
A way to avoid the problem is to have an action that tests the upgrade scripts

Changes proposed in this pull request:
- Create a new action "upgrade"
- Adjust pgtap tests that fail on previous versions because of
  -  bug fixes or 
  -  the functions/signatures do not belong to that version
- Modified the editor config to set SQL to 2 spaces
- And triggering the doc-check action only when documentation/translation changes
Note: this does not affect code so no pumping up to 3.2.1 yet, but I am setting the milestone to 3.2.1

@pgRouting/admins

Changes proposed in this pull request:
- Added `vrp_vroom` SQL functions:
- Added `vroom.c` file to convert postgres datatypes to C.
- Added vroom driver file and corresponding header file.
- Added sample boilerplate for pgTAP test.
- Updated typedefs and added vroom types structures.
- Updated CMakeLists temporarily so that tests don't fail on warnings.
- Updated configuration file, for compilation to include sql and src files of vroom.
